      "comment": "TIME TO PROPHET (1) raced just off the lead before letting down nicely and scoring a long neck win in a 68 over this journey at this track last time. Led and just missed at Townsville prior, and from a low gate can win again. MACHINE HEAD (7) resumes and has switched to the Trevor & Peter Rowe stable. Has decent form and performs fresh. Will use the rail to advantage and a bold return is likely. RUBY CHICKS (2) resumed and raced on the pace beaten 2.5 lengths over 1000m at Townsville. Will be better for that and has more up her sleeve. Has claims as well.  ZI WIN (3) resumes and has won 2/5 fresh. Like this track and trip and keep onside. GAMADALE NIP (6) resumes and filled a minor placing when returning from a spell last prep over 900m at Innisfail. Has a 2kg claim and is in the mix",
